data.description: Beautiful home with 10.5 ACRES! Solid beautifully remodeled brick home on 10.51 ACRES, green pastures include a wet weather pond. Detached brick recreation room with office/ shop & HVAC (could easily be a guest suite). Manicured & fertilized pastures with 3 paddocks that include water & solar electric fencing. The entrance has a solar remote GATE that leads you home via a long paved driveway. The whole house gas generator coveys. This property is perfect for a homesteading lifestyle. Updates include kitchen, plumbing, electrical, floors, windows, new well pump & so much more. Beautiful sunrises on the large covered back porch, and sunsets from the covered front porch; all overlooking pastures while you enjoy watching the turkey, deer, stars & more. Property taxes less than $600 yr, No HOA, located in the sought after rural & Historical Edgefield, where the southern charm abounds. 238 Meeting Street Rd.! FHA, USDA & VA loans welcomed!
